('66397','23097','5','Unique horse range with dressage school'),
('66398','23098','5','This estate is conveniently located in a quiet area, only 20 km away from Palma.\r\nThe property is set on a plot of about 28,000 m² and was created as a professional dressage and riding school of highest quality, where even international competitions could be held.\r\nThe features include: parking for horse trailers, two dressage arenas with special sand (measuring 60x20 m and 70x30 m, with referees house), computer based monitoring of the moisture level of riding surfaces, floodlight, lunging ring (18 m), 20 horse stables, tack room, locker rooms for riders, horse showers, box with heat lamps, 11 paddocks, private well including water treatment and automatic water supply for stables and many more.\r\nFurthermore, there are a wine cellar with bar and kitchen, and a house with two apartments (of 60 m² each), which need some renovation. The price is reduced from 1.995.000€ to 995.000€ !!!'),
